==English==
===Alternative spellings===
*sometimes hyphenated or expressed as a phrase: '''pan-theistical''', '''pan theistical'''
*sometimes either the P or both the P and the initial T are capitalized: '''Pantheistical''', '''PanTheistical'''
*variations of capitalization and spacing may be combined: '''Pan-theistical''', '''Pan-Theistical''', '''Pan Theistical''', '''Pan theistical'''
===Etymology===
From Greek Θεϊσμός
